data.description: WELCOME HOME to your commute friendly, affordable and updated home in Pacific! This 3 bedroom home offers more than the generous 1536 sqft, it also offers a large 2 car garage and huge .19 acre lot. This tri-level layout features main floor open living, kitchen and dining room with wood burning fireplace and tons of natural light. Upstairs features 3 bedrooms with 1.75 baths while the lower level offers a HUGE bonus room, 1/2 bath and laundry. Huge party deck off of the bonus room, fully fenced backyard even a great fire pit for those Friday night bonfires. Outbuildings for extra storage too. Great cul-de-sac location, minutes to easy HWY 167 access and bike to the nearby park!
